{"tid":232051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坂口健太郎「階梯之吻」撩妹　35cm最萌身高差超心動","createTime":"2017-05-06T13:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T13:28:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2c007d2ffb48a02760ed2ff481ccbe81643161","tid":232051,"uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"日本男星坂口健太郎與才女歌手miwa首次合作主演奇幻愛情電影《與妳的第100次戀愛》，身高184公分的坂口，與149公分的miwa整整有35公分的身高差，因此在片中有許多粉紅互動看起來都更加可愛；尤其一場在圖書館裡的「階梯之吻」，更是將浪漫氣息引爆到最高點。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2503/d2503381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2503%2Fd2503381.jpg&h=b8d2f303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲坂口健太郎與miwa的階梯之吻成經典。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2503/d2503382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2503%2Fd2503382.jpg&h=365df4e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2503/d2503383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2503%2Fd2503383.jpg&h=faf7f47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坂口健太郎在《與妳的第100次戀愛》中，時而穩重、時而浪漫，還大秀「撩妹連續技」，像是熱刺再戰打吡 卡尼當銳全力扑槌「不管妳跑得多快多遠，就算快要跌倒，我也會跑在妳前面，守護著妳。」等浪漫滿點的台詞，或是背後環抱、摸頭呵護、掌心貼掌心等舉動，都讓人少女心狂噴。他雖然在片中沒有使出「壁咚」必殺技，但卻創新上演「階梯之吻」，讓miwa站在圖書館的階梯上，輕輕抬起對方的下巴側頭一吻，場面令影迷超心動。"},{"pid":"48a9da11953a8b2fd5da85e9cc691ac4d2200a45","tid":232051,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d604910d6ce815f9237cd03c51acf650099348","tid":232051,"uid":109866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"佢真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f346958f6994fa77cade9